  "lesson": {
    "title": "Morse Code LED",
    "description": "Use one button as a Morse key. A quick tap (dot) and a longer press (dash) blink the LED. Try spelling S: three short, three long, three short. Timing is up to you — the circuit only turns the LED on while the button is held."
